Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:21.19,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,梅爾蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,這樣可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:25.22,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:26.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.06,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,再叫一次我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:30.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,梅爾蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,一定要保護好我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.92,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,然後就是…謝謝你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:39.46,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:42.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,不是…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:47.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,這個氣味…
